{"tid":1643599,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"POPO澄清文！","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:08:27.000Z","uid":244704,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8d43bbd8e6127d0125293cb4e34d34bee47bc5","tid":1643599,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"【屯門醫院就男警進入產房傳聞澄清】<br />\n<br />\n就網上有關男警進入產房的傳聞，屯門醫院發言人的澄清如下：<br />\n<br />\n該名孕婦在產房內的獨立檢查間內接受檢查，期間並沒有醫護人員以外的人士在場。<br />\n<br />\n由於該名孕婦由警察帶同入院，男警在護士及職員陪同下，曾到獨立檢查間與孕婦核對資料，完成後馬上離開檢查間，在產房內的家屬等候區等候。<br />\n<br />\n屯門醫院會致力確保病人私隱得到保障和病人服務運作暢順。<br />\n<br />\n澄清連結:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/pad/53718c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fhaho%2Fho%2Fpad%2F53718c.pdf&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=b7feb4c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/pad/53718c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n#造謠者居心叵測<br />\n#謠言就係講到好似真嘅一樣令你信<br />\n#警方一直重視任何人包括被捕人嘅私隱<br />\n#事件中警務人員從未進入過產房<br />\n#謠言止於智者"},{"pid":"d0c154557b8e3ab570dee31df1fb510b8e8c28c3","tid":1643599,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87eb0ba90bcbebcb83b3322f3deca8ecf202e1a1","tid":1643599,"uid":190604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"係政府信用破產嘅情況下<br />\n出段澄清就會信你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}